.TH "signal-handler routines" "" "" Overview
.PC
.PP
The following functions can be used by device drivers to handle signals:
.DS
.ta 1.5i
.tc . 0.1i
\fBactvsig()\fR	Activate signal handler
\fBnondsig()\fR	Non-default signal pending
\fBsendsig()\fR	Send a signal
\fBsigdump()\fR	Generate core dump
.DE
.SH "See Also"
.B
device drivers
.R
